headline: Dover (DOV) Enhances Fueling Efficiency with New Overfill Prevention Valve Launch
summary: Dover (DOV) recently experienced a notable development with its OPW Retail Fueling unit's launch of the 71SO Segmented Overfill Valve, which potentially supported the company's 18% share price movement in the last quarter. This product, with its enhanced design and efficiency benefits, promises to bolster safety and regulatory compliance, appealing to industry demands.
